
ImageMagick provides a most wonderful collection of graphic manipulation tools. For example, to change an image format:

	> convert image.png image.xpm

Or, to resize an image:

	> convert -resize 256x256 big.png small.png

Wow! Can it get any easier? - Yes it can:

	> convert -resize 256x256 big.png aWindowsIcon.ico

Resize and convert all in one step. Isn't that nice! 
